item.title: Website templates!
item.dc:creator: @The_Web_Guy The Web Guy
item.description:
@The_Web_Guy wrote:

Whether or not one is to like a template specifically pertains to their taste in design. Everyone has their own individual concept of what looks good, and what does not. Something I may find nice, you may not agree. Your best bet is to browse through the vBulletin templates and look at some previews and demos, then decide what YOU think looks good. Also, keep in mind what the site is for, you’re not going to want a pink fluffy flower template for a RSPS.
